 <text id="A6167T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Smith asks Flood to send him a shovel and some tongs.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1865-01-16">
       <abbr expan="January">Jany.</abbr> 16 1865</date>
      <name type="place">H<hi rend="super">
       <hi rend="underline">a</hi>
      </hi>
       <unclear>
        <abbr expan="Louisiana">Luis</abbr>
       </unclear>
       <unclear>
        <abbr expan="Engineers">Engis</abbr>
       </unclear>
       <unclear>
        <abbr expan="Valley Division">V.D.</abbr>
       </unclear>
      </name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><abbr expan="Lieutenant">Lieut.</abbr> M. E. Flood<lb/>
      <unclear>Amd.</unclear> Pioneer Party<lb/>
      <abbr expan="Lieutenant">Lieut.</abbr></salute>
    </opener>

    <p>Enclosed please find a furlough for Segt. J.E. <unclear>Belton</unclear></p>
    <p>When <orig reg="your">you</orig> Blacksmith has leisure please get him to make me a shoval
     &amp; pair of tongs-and if you can get me home some leather for a pair of <hi
      rend="underline">boots</hi> I'll be under obligations-</p>

    <closer>
     <salute>Yours</salute>
     <signed>Wm <hi rend="underline">Proctor</hi> Smith</signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
